  21,106,Inna fee hatha labalaghan liqawmin AAabideena
  21,107,Wama arsalnaka illa rahmatan lilAAalameena
  21,108,Qul innama yooha ilayya annama ilahukum ilahun wahidun fahal antum muslimoona
