  23,34,Walain ataAAtum basharan mithlakum innakum ithan lakhasiroona
  23,35,AyaAAidukum annakum itha mittum wakuntum turaban waAAithaman annakum mukhrajoona
  23,36,Hayhata hayhata lima tooAAadoona
